Subject: Re: [Flexradio] Weird BPSK31 Behavior

I would double check the sample rates between VAC on PowerSDR and on the VAC
lines in the Windows sound settings. If one is set to 48000 and the other to
44100, your signal would not look so good. Perhaps you're unexplained
shutdown reset something. I keep both at 48000.

Jim KA2RVO

